title: #254 - Bryan Callen & ME
description:
Comedian, podcaster, and actor Bryan Callen stops by the Mancave to talk about his new Special "NEVER GROW UP" airing on Amazon, Hulu, Google Play, XBOX, iTunes, Playstation, and practically everywhere,  we talk about him dating before he was married, acting, stand-up, Dov Davidoff, and I share everything I thought about him before I even met him.

To get info on Bryan's Special "NEVER GROW UP" go to www.TFATK.com

To get my book "Life of the Party" click HERE: https://www.amazon.com/Life-Party-Stories-Perpetual-Man-Child/dp/1250030250

For all TOUR DATE & MERCH click HERE: http://www.bertbertbert.com
